summary: I read this article somewhere that said that when they put Darth Vader's helmet on Anakin for the first time you can hear...
body:
I read this article somewhere that said that when they put Darth Vader’s helmet on Anakin for the first time you can hear “Padmé, help me!” if you listen very closely.

I can say I put up the volume at max. and I did hear Anakin’s voice screaming “Padmé”. I didn’t hear the rest but it gave me the chills nonetheless.

(also I might not have heard it because I’m pretty fucking deaf from turning my headphones up too loud when listening to music but whatever.)

summary: I was rewatching Friend in Need [TCW s04e14] which next part of Satine & Pre series in mind and during meeting between diplomats...
caption:
I was rewatching Friend in Need [TCW s04e14] which next part of Satine & Pre series in mind and during meeting between diplomats of Republic & CIS, there in background you can see painting from Pre’s residence on Concordia. Whoa. Why Satine would even need that for such important meeting and why it’s on Separatist side (while at the same time on the line of sight for Padme, Bail and Montha)? Even better question, how Duchess get hold on such thing? Wouldn’t it be confiscated by Concordian government and kept as evidence in an investigation against Vizsla’s betrayal or something like that?

Shame I didn’t remember that before I wrote meta about arts kept by Satine & Pre in their residences. On other hand, it makes me feel like I was right, this mural is not about violence but about protecting Mandalorian City (culture/peope) if it is used now to remind Bail, Padme and Montha (diplomats) that their Republic is not saint and has a dark (violent) past too.

summary: Solo: A Star Wars Story
title: Solo: A Star Wars Story
body:
imdb

Vagány heist mozi, ezerszer látott fordulatokkal. Éppenhogy kibírható főszereplővel. Az eleje szar, a közepe unalmas, a vége nem rossz.

Plot: Indiana Jones visszamegy a messzi-messzi jövőbe, hogy megdugjon egy szőrös majmot, de végül kiderül, hogy mindketten mást szeretnek. A legjobb karakter egy metroszexuális, a gazdája szerint nő robot, ami egyrészt erős kontrasztba rakja az üzenetet és feloldhatatlan feszültséget okoz a suffragette és fekete egyenjogúság terén. Az egyetlen létező film ahol bizonyított tény, hogy a pöcsköszörű létezik és használható eszköz.

  • + pöcsköszörű, AI által generált random lények
  • - az őstrilógiából unalomig ismételt szófordulatok, nincsenek nácik
